description.en:
HE ECONOMIC COIN FOR GLOBAL TRADING FINANCIAL INSTRUMENT ISSUANCE AND PROCESSING - "ONE COIN TWO BLOCKCHAINS"

Encocoin is a fork of Dash blockchain by the Encocoin core developers and with great supports from established blockchain consultants.

Encocoin blockchain project is an initiative and an attempt by the Encocoin Foundation to create a new international trade(import and exports) financial instrument and payment system instead of the manual paper based cumbersome bank guarantees, letters of credits and real estates holding documents currently in practice.

Encocoin mission is to use it's blockchain distributed ledger to integrate imports and exports banking instruments into cryptographic based and escrow-able economic financial digital asset.The eventual Encocoin blockchain application will successfully eliminate the need for the current paper based financial documents.

•   Everyone running the Encocoin masternode starts earning rewards same day.
•   All masternodes purchased through our collaborating partners are indemnified against capital loss.
